# KLab Cursor rules
#
# This repo uses Cursor Project Rules in `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`.
# If you are seeing this file, it’s only a compatibility shim for older Cursor
# setups. The real, scoped rules live in `.cursor/rules/`.
#
# - Global guardrails: `.cursor/rules/00-guardrails.mdc`
# - File-scoped rules auto-attach based on globs (compose, docs, scripts, workflows)
# - Task playbooks are agent-requested rules (new stack, upgrades, exposure, migrations)
